From the manufacturer

Why Instax Film

With dazzling instant iconic-framed prints, stunning colour and professional high-quality film technology, we ask you why not?

Only compatible with instax products - mini 9, mini 11, mini 40, mini 70, mini 90, mini Evo, mini LiPlay, and mini Link.

Instax Mini Deco Film

Mini moments with maximum impact, What's your mini moment?

Make your instant photos even more fun with the creative Deco instax mini film with coloured borders. Each pack contains 10 shots of high quality credit-card sized photos that you can fit into a purse, wallet or mini photo frame.

Instax Mini Film Monochrome

See differently

In a world full of colour, our black and white instant film offers not just a timeless quality to your memories, but also the chance to explore tone, contrast, shadow and composition.

Product description

Product Description

Bring on the film - make your instant photos even more fun with the classic instax mini film with white border. Each pack contains 10 shots of high quality credit-card sized photos that you can fit into a purse, wallet or mini photo frame. Your pictures will be incredibly sharp thanks to the high-speed ISO 800 film made for the instax mini series cameras and printers. Recognised for its high quality colour reproduction, the instax mini film has a glossy finish, is simple to use and easy to load. Print size - 54 x 86 mm, Imagesize: 46 x 62 mm.

Manufacturer's Description

Two 10 shoot Film packs for Fujifilm Instax Mini Cameras

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
